    {
      "id": "port-canva-metaphor",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Core Metaphor",
      "position": {
        "x": 460,
        "y": -160
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Core Metaphor\n\nPorts are **attachment grammar**.\n\nThey should feel like:\n- sockets\n- notches\n- tabs\n- pin recesses\n\nThey should not feel like:\n- buttons\n- badges\n- mini nodes\n- bright floating circles",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
