    {
      "id": "port-canva-idle",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Idle State",
      "position": {
        "x": 900,
        "y": -220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Idle State\n\nAt rest, ports should be barely there.\n\nGoal:\n- imply availability without stealing attention\n\nDesired feel:\n- subtle boundary notch\n- low contrast\n- small footprint\n- no loud color",
