    {
      "id": "port-canva-hover",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Hover State",
      "position": {
        "x": 1280,
        "y": -220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Hover State\n\nOn hover, the port should become clearly legible.\n\nGoal:\n- confirm that this is the attachment point\n\nDesired feel:\n- slightly brighter\n- slightly larger\n- more contrast\n- optional short label or hint",
        "_classBinding": {
