    {
      "id": "port-canva-drag",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Drag Target State",
      "position": {
        "x": 1660,
        "y": -220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Drag Target State\n\nDuring connection drag, the port should feel magnetic and trustworthy.\n\nGoal:\n- make drop confidence immediate\n\nDesired feel:\n- stronger glow or highlight\n- obvious socket target\n- clear magnetic emphasis\n- still cleaner than a big glowing button",
        "_classBinding": {
