    {
      "id": "port-canva-connected",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Connected State",
      "position": {
        "x": 2040,
        "y": -220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Connected State\n\nA connected port should show occupancy calmly.\n\nGoal:\n- indicate that the relationship exists\n- avoid screaming once the edge is established\n\nDesired feel:\n- quieter than hover\n- visibly occupied\n- stable and low-noise",
